11#include "video/transport_adapter.h"
12
13#include "rtc_base/checks.h"
14
15namespace webrtc {
16namespace internal {
17
18TransportAdapter::TransportAdapter(Transport* transport)
19 : transport_(transport), enabled_(false) {
20 RTC_DCHECK(nullptr != transport);
21}
22
23TransportAdapter::~TransportAdapter() = default;
24
25bool TransportAdapter::SendRtp(const uint8_t* packet,
26 size_t length,
27 const PacketOptions& options) {
28 if (!enabled_.load())
29 return false;
30
31 return transport_->SendRtp(packet, length, options);
32}
33
34bool TransportAdapter::SendRtcp(const uint8_t* packet, size_t length) {
35 if (!enabled_.load())
36 return false;
37
38 return transport_->SendRtcp(packet, length);
39}
40
41void TransportAdapter::Enable() {
42 enabled_.store(true);
43}
44
45void TransportAdapter::Disable() {
46 enabled_.store(false);
47}
48
49} // namespace internal
50} // namespace webrtc
